    <h1>Heading Tags (H1-H6)</h1>
    <p class="description">HTML elements that create a hierarchical content structure on web pages. <strong>58% of pages ranking in Google's top 10</strong> use H2 and H3 tags matching related search queries (Semrush, 1.2M pages). Critical for rankings, featured snippets, and accessibility.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
