            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>One H1 per page is the SEO best practice. HTML5 technically allows multiple H1s, but for Google to receive a clear content signal, a single H1 containing your primary keyword is standard. Multiple H1s can confuse crawlers about the page's primary topic.</p></div></div>
          </div>
